title: Why am i not unranked yet?
body: When do we get to play the 10 ranked games to determine our rank.

replies.body:
If you're talking about season 8, that hasn't started yet. We're still in preseason so it's still going to show your rank from season 7.

We'll keep our [news page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) updated for when season 8 starts, so hang tight! :)
So i can go crazy in ranked?
